WEBVTT

00:01.085 --> 00:02.362
ï»¿Who's my good boy?

00:02.938 --> 00:03.937
I had the perfect life.

00:07.157 --> 00:07.721
Until one day,...

00:08.278 --> 00:09.209
All yours, little guy.

00:09.599 --> 00:10.383
...everything changed.

00:13.547 --> 00:14.446
There's been a mistake!

00:15.655 --> 00:16.202
Nina!

00:16.323 --> 00:17.069
Ferdinand!

00:18.435 --> 00:20.183
Now, I know when you look at me, you think "big."

00:20.297 --> 00:21.413
You're ginormous!

00:21.532 --> 00:23.346
I can't wait to show you to the rest of the guys.

00:23.507 --> 00:25.033
They're gonna fertilize the yard.

00:25.217 --> 00:26.215
It's scary.

00:27.273 --> 00:27.761
Who are you?

00:27.875 --> 00:28.511
I'm Uno.

00:28.749 --> 00:29.396
I'm Dos.

00:29.511 --> 00:30.365
And I'm Quatro.

00:30.488 --> 00:31.190
What happened to Tres?

00:32.127 --> 00:33.083
We do not speak of Tres.

00:34.635 --> 00:35.753
You think someone who could fight.

00:35.847 --> 00:37.208
I am here to select a bull.

00:37.574 --> 00:38.315
I'll take that one.

00:38.403 --> 00:39.999
Sucks to be you!

00:40.061 --> 00:41.983
I am not a fighting bull!

00:42.061 --> 00:43.179
Can you guys help me out?

00:43.356 --> 00:47.519
This is the beautiful horsey side and that is the stinky bull side.

00:47.631 --> 00:49.622
Have a nice day smelling terrible!

00:49.853 --> 00:50.457
High hooves, Klaus.

00:50.579 --> 00:51.269
High hooves, Greta.

00:54.103 --> 00:54.821
Nina needs me.

00:55.214 --> 00:56.445
I'm getting out of this place...

00:56.612 --> 00:57.839
...and I'm not leaving anyone behind.

00:58.063 --> 00:59.411
Best plan ever!

00:59.557 --> 01:01.220
Just do exactly what we do.

01:09.351 --> 01:10.759
Maybe don't do exactly as we do.

